Find the year anchor. Starting with year Y:
 - note the century anchor A
 - take the last two digits T = Y % 100
 - if odd, add eleven T = T + (T % 2)*11
 - then divide by two T = T / 2
 - if odd, add eleven T = T + (T % 2)*11
 - subtract from seven T = 7 - T
 - add the century anchor to get W = A + T
